The paper presents a system for recognising human activity using a symbolic representation of video content. This involves the use of a probabilistic logic programming framework to handle uncertainty. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
